    { q: "The ultimate benefit of good career research and planning is:", options: ["A fulfilling, successful and satisfying career", "Unemployment", "Frequent job changes", "Frustration"], ans: "A fulfilling, successful and satisfying career", topic: "Career Research and Planning" }
